snippet.title: Wuthering Waves Version 2.1 Geographic Preview
snippet.description:
Wuthering Waves Version 2.1 "Waves Sing, and the Cerulean Bird Calls" is set to launch on February 13 (UTC+8)!
Before diving into the new areas Riccioli Islands & Averardo Vault: Underground Depository coming on Version 2.1, let's take a sneak peek at what they look like!
